<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q28_v10" title="Q28_v10" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Para regular la rapidez con la que se suministra suero a un paciente, se utiliza un dispositivo llamado bomba de infusión.</p>
    <p>Esta rapidez <m:math><m:mi>r</m:mi></m:math>, medida en mililitros por hora (ml/h), se modela con la expresión <m:math><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:mfrac></m:math>, donde <m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi></m:math> es el volumen del suero, en ml, y <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:math> es la cantidad de horas en que se suministra la totalidad del suero.</p>
    <p>La bomba de infusión se programó para administrar el suero durante 30 minutos (es decir, 0,5 horas) con una rapidez de 1200 ml/h. ¿Qué volumen total de suero se administrará en ese tiempo?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">300 ml<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si el volumen fuera <m:math><m:mn>300</m:mn></m:math> ml en <m:math><m:mn>0,5</m:mn></m:math> horas, entonces la rapidez sería <m:math><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mn>0,5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>600</m:mn></m:math> ml/h, que no coincide con <m:math><m:mn>1200</m:mn></m:math> ml/h.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">600 ml<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! De <m:math><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:mfrac></m:math> se obtiene <m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:math>. Entonces, <m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>0,5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>600</m:mn></m:math> ml.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">1200 ml<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si el volumen fuera <m:math><m:mn>1200</m:mn></m:math> ml en <m:math><m:mn>0,5</m:mn></m:math> horas, entonces la rapidez sería <m:math><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mn>0,5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2400</m:mn></m:math> ml/h, que no coincide con <m:math><m:mn>1200</m:mn></m:math> ml/h.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">2400 ml<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si el volumen fuera <m:math><m:mn>2400</m:mn></m:math> ml en <m:math><m:mn>0,5</m:mn></m:math> horas, entonces la rapidez sería <m:math><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>2400</m:mn><m:mn>0,5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4800</m:mn></m:math> ml/h, que no coincide con <m:math><m:mn>1200</m:mn></m:math> ml/h.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar los datos</strong></p>
            <p>La rapidez es <m:math><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn></m:math> ml/h y el tiempo es 30 minutos, es decir, <m:math><m:mn>0,5</m:mn></m:math> horas.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Usar la relación entre rapidez, volumen y tiempo</strong></p>
            <p>Se tiene <m:math><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:mfrac></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Despejando <m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi></m:math>, resulta <m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Reemplazar los valores</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>0,5</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Calcular</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>0,5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>600</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El volumen total de suero administrado en ese tiempo es <m:math><m:mn>600</m:mn></m:math> ml. Por lo tanto, la alternativa correcta es la <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>